# zara-jira-mcp

AI-powered Scrum Master MCP server with 124 tools.

## First Use

Call `jira_boards` to get board_id.

## Key Tools

- `pm_standup_prep(board_id)` — daily standup prep
- `pm_planning_prep(board_id)` — sprint planning
- `pm_sprint_health(board_id)` — health score
- `pm_forecast(board_id, remaining_items:N)` — Monte Carlo forecast
- `pm_exec_report(board_id)` — executive report (never pm_dashboard for execs)
- `pm_snapshot_sprint(board_id, velocity:N)` — end-of-sprint capture
- `pm_record_risk/decision/blocker` — record immediately
- `pm_auto_detect_risks(board_id)` — weekly risk scan
- `pm_anti_patterns(board_id)` — detect team dysfunctions

## Architecture

Go 1.26, uber-go/fx DI, SQLite WAL, mcp-go transport.
Domain-driven: domain/ (interfaces), internal/ (implementations), application/tools/ (handlers).

